headline: Zimmer Biomet Announces Webcast and Conference Call of First Quarter 2025 Financial Results
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH) today announced its first quarter earnings conference call will be webcast on Monday, May 5, 2025, at 8:30 a.m. ET. A news release detailing the quarterly results will be made available that day at 6:30 a.m. ET.
